{"tid":415143,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]解決iPhone8黃mon問題","createTime":"2017-09-26T17:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T01:30:07.000Z","uid":5793,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1f72d5c06ec7e9279dbd86c9524449b009b6614d","tid":415143,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:44:29.000Z","msg":"用左2日都係覺得個mon黃<br />\n<br />\n已經熄左true tone同埋自動調整亮度個啲林甚野<br />\n<br />\n心諗點解仲會咁黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網睇下有冇土炮方法可以教，發現原來仲有招可以手動調色教返正常白色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n方法如下：<br />\n設定&gt;一般&gt;輔助使用&gt;顯示器調節&gt;顏色濾鏡&gt;色調(跟我張圖咁拉條bar 強度+色相兩條都要)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/014104_dcf5bf7d3fad6a1ede90bf178031442b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F014104_dcf5bf7d3fad6a1ede90bf178031442b.jpg&h=f84f25f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niPhone8又可以繼續開心使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幫到你嘅就正個皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525bf9af29e3e8d2f047be9d6a03c84f7c067682","tid":415143,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea4fd3471df84d23417e117199d497f1f469d03","tid":415143,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20431802657601b19664040ee942c21824cf75b","tid":415143,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7077cf65fe2497e0101458feb736bf722ce49cab","tid":415143,"uid":19072,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:48:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c70534c4bb0865fafe9538e6ef3736669f148f4b","tid":415143,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔cap出黎點知黃成點？</blockquote><br />\n睇下有冇其他巴絲打影低個對比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我已經set好曬唔想重新教過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係希望幫到有需要嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ce398acb9f75d8b6a634200cf62ce201ba1f18","tid":415143,"uid":120537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:50:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔cap出黎點知黃成點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb84230d4c509b3d23429ca5849a005445eb09ab","tid":415143,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔cap出黎點知黃成點？</blockquote><br />\n呢個係教學嚟㗎"},{"pid":"7e16188e226e3dbceb857fb26ecb6c583729f9c9","tid":415143,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:52:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你唔cap出黎點知黃成點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢係咪想伏我 同一張圖唔同機出嘅色都唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCap就一定睇唔到對比 要2部機拍埋一齊影張相先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfefb4ae6c7e72716976e4da92e45c21cfa87c3","tid":415143,"uid":19072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:52:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15b8acea4dce957ca56eeffecf75c570e6024d73","tid":415143,"uid":149931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8692106a53e3a0f3560fa42b975a64a8d2750ecc","tid":415143,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你唔cap出黎點知黃成點？</blockquote><br />\n呢個係教學嚟㗎</blockquote><br />\n教學都可以cap張前後對比圖黎睇下</blockquote><br />\n應該你唔會睇到有分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為係個mon display啲色出黎 <br />\n唔關我本身點set事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似係 戴定頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc517c9f3d0f41b7cdee3e56b449a4cb611c5e0","tid":415143,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:57:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你唔cap出黎點知黃成點？</blockquote><br />\n呢個係教學嚟㗎</blockquote><br />\n教學都可以cap張前後對比圖黎睇下</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/015613_4491a246d015e79de2d3ba309a2ca9c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F015613_4491a246d015e79de2d3ba309a2ca9c0.jpg&h=5ca51dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身呢個功能預設係關閉左 開左佢就係咁嘅畫面<br />\n<br />\n你係咪想睇呢張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013dec8fa2e8ebadd55177341a2400222b253adb","tid":415143,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T18:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6582ff36d8e796eeb382305cba4d10eb37ccddd6","tid":415143,"uid":150118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T18:15:32.000Z","msg":"78千買部機仲要自己搞色水<br />\n真係慘過閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b50cbc94f93dee296d98d996e1200b5996eeb20","tid":415143,"uid":1130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T18:23:53.000Z","msg":"之前有個巴打 問我地見唔見個mon有黑影定唔知咩<br />\n但佢掉張cap圖出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad4748ed2f7dc689faac1c51f406f5e33198365","tid":415143,"uid":6953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T18:46:44.000Z","msg":"p3廣色域個mon 係會暖色d.呢個白平衡會準d"},{"pid":"08c15b8b506bf885cd018d5a4c47984c60acfb31","tid":415143,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>78千買部機仲要自己搞色水<br />\n真係慘過閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得搞都好過冇得搞要硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5166648b5a3ea85d42990d56c77cda709292bc6e","tid":415143,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:36:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前有個巴打 問我地見唔見個mon有黑影定唔知咩<br />\n但佢掉張cap圖出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a8b9a89b1ecd65bc9af21463ac896a3a4ac1c2","tid":415143,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:57:48.000Z","msg":"又係呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nse 用到宜家"},{"pid":"d527a5c78a5e0fd6e7f218b872cb24b2bec82c37","tid":415143,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T00:04:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nse 用到宜家</blockquote>